Paladin of Erollisi Marr <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ucwynlaen.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Cwynlaen</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_fire.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 3<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(5/20/02 9:47:31 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=681.topic&index=21>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Really?</span><hr size=1> I haven't been on this server very long... just slightly before the May 8th patch really.  I'm ready to hotkey &quot;/shout /autojoin chat&quot; already.  I guess I'll have to go back to my practice on the others servers and start turning more channels off.<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/uarkitip.showPublicProfile?language=EN>arkitip</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 238<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(5/21/02 1:38:45 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=681.topic&index=22>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Really?</span><hr size=1> Never shouted SoW plz in my life.<br>
So here's your question:<br>
Ever tried hunting High Shaman Phido?<br>
Like I said, until you have, don't go bitching that someone is being helpful by shouting out that a mob that would do them no good to kill but would make a monk's day is roaming.<br>
<br>
To you that may seem like a &quot;fun&quot; aspect of the game. To me, there's no fun being had by randomly wandering the western half of Southern Karana looking for one gnoll that may or may not be around. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ukloeviseq.showPublicProfile?language=EN>KloevisEQ</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 174<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(5/21/02 1:56:28 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=681.topic&index=23>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://web.cci.clarku.edu/ebarry/pix1.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Really?</span><hr size=1> I don't think it's unreasonable to try and look for something yourself. Guess what? Every class and every race can find something in a zone.<br>
The fun is when you're looking for something, and you get it your damned self, instead of relying on every single fucking person in the zone to suit your needs-<br>
<br>
&quot;where is X_mob?&quot;<br>
&quot;SOW PLZ&quot;<br>
&quot;Crack me plz&quot;<br>
&quot;Can I get a REZ?&quot;<br>
I swear, it goes beyond helping someone, when all you hear is this shit shouted zone-wide every fucking 2 minutes. <br>
<br>
This is a videogame. Are you some sort of fucking moron who can't do a goddamned thing for yourself?<br>
Ever think &quot;Gosh, maybe there's people who would like to try and do it on their own&quot; or maybe they LIKE hunting. Thanks. You just shouted the &quot;whodunit&quot; in a movie theater. Same deal.<br>
<br>
Someone sees me with my pet they think &quot;Oh! Chanter! He can breeze/bind/buff&quot;<br>
and I get a direct tell from some stranger asking me to drop my shit and make his game easier for him.<br>
Why do you even bother playing if you couldn't do something yourself? Maybe it's laziness. I don't know, but this shit spoils the fun for some people, and that's why I think it sucks.<br>
<br>
 <p><img src="http://web.cci.clarku.edu/ebarry/ban.jpg"></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ubakanome.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Bakanome</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 137<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(5/21/02 2:56:01 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=681.topic&index=24>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Really?</span><hr size=1> Alright, maybe I may have been premature.  I'm going to have to look around the EC tunnel again.  If anything pops up there, there ain't no fricking way they're getting it started on here while I'm around. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ulunathreee.showPublicProfile?language=EN>lunathreee</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 10<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(5/21/02 1:46:58 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=681.topic&index=25>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Really?</span><hr size=1> question from the ignorant *raises hand*<br>
